\prod_{k=0}^{n-1} \left\lvert \sin\left( z + \frac{k\pi}{n}\right)\right\rvert^2 = \left\lvert \frac{\sin (nz)}{2^{n-1}}\right\rvert^2 = \frac{\lvert \sin (nz)\rvert^2}{2^{2n-2}}.
