X^n - 1
(2)
e^{i\pi(n-1)/2} = i^{n-1}
\prod_{k=0}^{n-1} \sin \left( x + \frac{k\pi}{n}\right) = \frac{e^{-inx}\left(e^{2inx}-1\right)}{2^ni} = \frac{e^{inx} - e^{-inx}}{2^ni} = \frac{\sin (nx)}{2^{n-1}}.
